&lt;li&gt;Consistent achievement of monthly and annual account targets&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Deep fluency in grocery retail metrics and account health indicators&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Proactive identification and resolution of risk, issues, and underperformance&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
