&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Have genuine fluency in retail or grocery — merchandising, store ops, catalog data, and how enterprise grocers make decisions&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Lead with evidence: vet opportunities with data before committing a team, then drive hard to ship&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Are direct, low ego, and energized by defining a category in a lean, fast-moving organization&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
