&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Define and drive the roadmap for Flashfood&#39;s retail platform: partner app, onboarding and activation, catalog integration, dashboards and reporting, and dynamic pricing.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Bring deep retail domain knowledge into every planning cycle so roadmap calls are grounded in how grocers actually operate.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Vet the biggest opportunities with data, size them, and sequence them — your first two quarters set the build plan and the hires that follow.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;h3&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Lead a Cross-Functional Team&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Directly manage the Retail pod — engineers, product managers, and designers — with an engineering lead as your player-coach on architecture.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Own the pod&#39;s business goals: stores activated, items posted, partner adoption, and the revenue tied to them.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Sequence team growth behind validated opportunities, and set the bar across functions: crisp specs, sound tradeoffs, measurable outcomes, honest post-launch reads.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
